  <prompt>The workspace launcher (`LegalWorkspaceApp` mount hook or equivalent) reads `autoPopup` preference on mount and opens the Daily Briefing tab automatically if true. Adjust if a different shell owns this — confirm during pre-flight inspection.</prompt>
  <role>SPAARKE platform developer. Follow ADRs strictly. Expert in Fluent UI v9 + React hooks + Xrm.WebApi.</role>
  <goal>When user lands on workspace with `autoPopup=true`, Daily Briefing tab is selected/opened automatically on mount. When `autoPopup=false`, default tab logic applies (no change from current behavior).</goal>
  <context>
    <background>FR-17d: `autoPopup` preference must produce a real workspace-mount-time behavior change. Per spec assumption, `LegalWorkspaceApp` mount hook is the integration point. Verify via Grep first.</background>
