  </outputs>
  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">autoPopup=true → Daily Briefing tab auto-opens on workspace mount (FR-17d / AC-17d)</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">autoPopup=false → no behavior change vs current workspace launcher</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
  <ui-tests>
    <test>Set autoPopup=true; reload workspace; verify Daily Briefing tab is active without click</test>
    <test>Set autoPopup=false; reload workspace; verify default tab logic applies</test>
    <test>Toggle preference; reload; verify behavior switches per setting</test>
    <test>Dark Mode Compliance: workspace + DB tab render in dark theme; ADR-021 semantic tokens used</test>
    <test>Console Errors: no errors during workspace mount + auto-tab-selection</test>
  </ui-tests>
  <notes>Spec assumption is `LegalWorkspaceApp` — verify before editing. If wrong, document actual shell in notes/ and adjust. Mount-once is critical: don't re-trigger on re-render. R3 PR #451 file overlap — run conflict-check.</notes>
